to set up a roommate group: 1. each person in the roommate group needs to login to the portal to complete the web profile page. you must click the box in order to be included in the roommate search. also give your screen name to the group leader at this time. 2. the group leader then logs back into the portal to create a roommate group name and password. 3. the group leader then adds all roommates to the group. the group leader will need to know the screen names of everyone in the group, please get these from your roommates. 4. the group leader must verify the group- click on "verify group" in order to do this. the group is now set up and is complete and ready for room selection. mon - fri 8:00am-5:00pm pst 